{
  "stem": "1363.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was taken away from them nice and slowly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we were very liberal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must agree that we didn't keep a Friday night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't observe it at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the other hand, both my brothers and my became bar mitzvah and bat mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] No, both my brother and I became bar mitzvah and bat mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was more so a pushing of my uncle-- a great-uncle, my grandmother's cousin, I think, twice removed-- who said that he definitely-- he was a religious man and had a kosher household, and financially, very nicely liquid.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he supported wherever he could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he pushed his foot down that the two of us have to have our bat mitzvah and bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, we only had the two to three high holy days in the year, which as you know, the Pesach, and Rosh Hashanah, and Yom Kippur was always there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact-- well, I will tell you after.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Yom Kippur, I had a very nasty experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the war, they were-- I kept the Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I collapsed in the toilet about 3:00 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was forever and ever after taken off-- I'm not allowed to diet, meaning fast.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, oh, yes, high holy days we always kept.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we didn't have the Friday night rituals, or the Saturday morning going to synagogue, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did pick up the telephone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Budapest, there were mixed and majority very [? neoliberal ?] people, where there are-- there were quite a few who were very religious and had a kosher household.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But these things were more in the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The city, big city, people were more liberal.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
